sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend<br/>(React)
    participant BE as Backend<br/>(FastAPI)
    participant LLM as Azure OpenAI<br/>(GPT-4.1)

    Note over U,LLM: AGENT CHAT WITH FUNCTION-CALLING

    U->>FE: 1. Type message in chat
    FE->>BE: 2. POST /api/agent/chat<br/>{messages, presentation_id, slide_index}

    BE->>BE: 3. Build messages:<br/>system prompt + slide context + history

    loop Up to 5 tool-calling iterations
        BE->>LLM: 4. chat.completions.create<br/>(tools: 5 functions, tool_choice: auto)
        LLM-->>BE: 5. Response

        alt LLM returns tool_calls
            Note over BE: Tool dispatch
            BE->>BE: 6. Execute tool(s):<br/>• translate_slide_notes<br/>• detect_text_language<br/>• ask_about_slides<br/>• generate_avatar_speech_ssml<br/>• prepare_slide_for_presentation
            BE->>LLM: 7. Append tool results → next iteration
        else LLM returns final answer
            BE-->>FE: 8. Return {reply: "..."}
        end
    end

    FE-->>U: 9. Display assistant response
